title: UNITEK superspeed USB 3.0 Multi in 1 Card Reader for CF/TF/Mrico SD/SD/MD/MMC/SDHC/SDXC for macbook pro mac
description: UNITEK Y-9313 is a superspeed USB 3.0 Multi in 1 Card Reader for CF/TF/Mrico SD/SD/MD/MMC/SDHC/SDXC use. Work well on macbook pro.SuperSpeed USB 3.0 devices supports transfer rates up to 5 Gbps. Backwards compatible with USB 2.0.Supports multiple cards to use at the some time, more easily for information exchangeSpecifications:- USB (Universal Serial Bus) v3.0 Specification- Truly Plug & Play and Hot swapping capabilityFast Data/Files Access and Transfer Rate Super-Speed (5Gps) / High-Speed (480Mbps) / Full-Speed (12 Mbps)- Draw Power directly from USB3.0 Port- Support SDXC 2TB- Micro SD no need adaptorPLEASE NOTE:1.SD card and TF card sharing one channel can not be read simultaneously;2.The card reader can only read one of the card when cards sharing the same slot at the same time.Package includes:- 1 x USB 3.0 Card Reader
